neCount > 1`\n\nThat would answer the product question directly without collecting creepy detail. Keep names boring and low-cardinality.","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-06-04T22:26:26.043Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","phase":"final_answer"}}}